src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你點知嫁</blockquote><br />\n甲狀腺主要通過吸收身體內的碘，而將其轉化成三碘甲狀腺氨酸T3和甲狀腺素T4。T3和T4調節新陳代謝、生長速率及血壓、心跳等。T3和T4由碘和酪胺酸合成。甲狀腺也生產降鈣素（Calcitonin），調節體內鈣的平衡。<br />\n又稱大頸泡，利申屋企人食野好淡，試過患上了"},{"pid":"d4eb90ac49389aa4348c2b6a391568510d884df9","tid":127472,"uid":11970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T09:58:44.000Z","msg":"有手震 冇乜手汗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有排懷疑係我練樂器太多<br />\n唔知關唔關事"},{"pid":"c276b8b291f2da41577d0cc11db9a37f1ba99c87","tid":127472,"uid":64564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T10:14:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>check下係咪甲狀腺，手震出汗心跳快典型病徵黎</blockquote><br />\n一分鐘平均90-100下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  甲狀腺會點<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41eb8c025fca0e2f915748cc9c5912eaafa3f8eb","tid":127472,"uid":11970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T10:15:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>check下係咪甲狀腺，手震出汗心跳快典型病徵黎</blockquote><br />\n一分鐘平均90-100下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  甲狀腺會點<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n跳得好快<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25f131dd741dd99bc1c6a98ff3a44ce048f3dbcb","tid":127472,"uid":64564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T10:45:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>check下係咪甲狀腺，手震出汗心跳快典型病徵黎</blockquote><br />\n一分鐘平均90-100下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  甲狀腺會點<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n跳得好快<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile_big.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 都唔知點解"},{"pid":"56fd17e011c4b0cfb12981c7f2d01140420640ce","tid":127472,"uid":86340,"like":0,"dislike